attributes.Long form description: The student assembles the white legs, and the student tightens the middle bolt and the hex nut with a spanner wrench. After that, the student inspects the white leg. The student places the white legs on the seat. The student puts the four screws and saddle washers on, and the student tightens the screws from the leg of the chair.

attributes.Transcription: Now we're looking at some IKEA furniture.
